&ldquo;
  <span>We're a group of IT professionals and job seekers who meet on the 4th Wednesday of every month at the Tavern in the Square, in Central Square, Cambridge</span>&rdquo;

<p>Agenda:</p>
<p>6:00 - 6:30 pm: &nbsp;Refreshments and networking&nbsp;
 <br />6:30 - 7:00 pm: &nbsp;Individual introductions to the group&nbsp;(who you are / what you're looking for)
 <br />7:00 - 7:30 pm: &nbsp;Job hunting tips
 <br />&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - who's hiring / interviewing&nbsp;
 <br />&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - tools and technologies / what's hot, what's not
 <br />&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - job hunting resources, other places to look&nbsp;
 <br />7:30 - 8:00 pm: &nbsp;More networking / information exchange</p>
<p>If you're a hiring manager, recruiter, or entrepreneur looking to hire staff, please feel free to bring along handouts about your company and open positions and/or business cards. Looking forward to seeing you all there!</p>
